{"tid":866324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"工藤貼身報行蹤 光希紅唇look夠青春","createTime":"2018-10-17T18:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:02:36.000Z","uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7656cbcda7f1532b98ab3aa97d7361c7388427","tid":866324,"uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"木村光希來咗香港兩日，今日就正式登場，以代言人身份出席品牌活動。化咗紅唇look的光希，青春無敵！一出場就閃爆，由於她的經理人事前已聲明齋影相唔會有訪問，店内亦不能拍照，但光希在台上禮貌地同傳媒問好！佢話：「第一次來香港，香港係好美麗嘅城市，我有去了些地方參觀⋯⋯」當然再一輪多謝品牌邀請之類的官方說話，唔夠三十秒，完！<br />\n<br />\n不過，要知光希在香港搞乜做乜？就要多謝佢媽媽工藤靜香喇！點解？因為佢貼身陪住女兒外，仲貼身拍下女兒行程，仲上埋ig嘅即時動態，所以大家就知光希今天去咗街邊小店買雞蛋仔，然後下午返酒店化妝，準備去中環⋯⋯貼身報告！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pXOlFf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pXOlFf&d=qJafdh2PD12xFIro0Oi7zJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=43c8fdce\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pXOlFf</a>"},{"pid":"3890492fb63465f1198ec5f5a3cb75f3180fbdc6","tid":866324,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/024007_f2ff1db155f51ac9e43f7d11d54e4bee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F024007_f2ff1db155f51ac9e43f7d11d54e4bee.jpg&h=0ef031b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d4c39fffb9174c08d9c31c0f3c43e53791eec53","tid":866324,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3890492fb63465f1198ec5f5a3cb75f3180fbdc6","tid":866324,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/024007_f2ff1db155f51ac9e43f7d11d54e4bee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F024007_f2ff1db155f51ac9e43f7d11d54e4bee.jpg&h=0ef031b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa